portTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2525742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2525742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104akv1665702559054.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/akv1665702559054.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/akv1665702559054.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"akv1665702559054\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"akv1665702559054___valrep_300500\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set the ValRep used by a widget for a field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"akv1665702559054__topic_d91403e1_d91404e1_d91405e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__p_d91406e1_d91407e1_d91408e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$valrep</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__p_d91409e1_d91410e1_d91411e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$valrep</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__section_N10068_N1001F_N10001\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__p_d91412e1_d91413e1_d91414e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$valrep(COLORS.THEME) = \"R=Red<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>G=Green<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>B=Blue\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"akv1665702559054__topic_d60842e1_d60843e1_d60844e1_d60845e1_d60846e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d932805e118\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__3\">Field name; optional; can be a literal name, a\n                        string, or a variable, function, parameter or indirect reference to a field.\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> can optionally contain a qualified field name,\n                        for example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">MYFLD.MYENT</code>. If omitted, the current field is\n                        used. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"akv1665702559054__table_d10118e1_d10119e1_d10120e1__entry__3\">\n Associative list that contains the desired ValRep items for the specified field\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"akv1665702559054__topic_d60847e1_d60848e1_d60849e1_d60850e1_d60851e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d932805e193\">Return Values </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"akv1665702559054__li_d36116e1_d36117e1_d36118e1\">ValRep list used by a widget for the specified field.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"akv1665702559054__li_d36119e1_d36120e1_d36121e1\">Empty string (\"\"), if no ValRep list has been declared or if the field cannot be found.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"akv1665702559054__topic_d60852e1_d60853e1_d60854e1_d60855e1_d60856e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d932805e209\">Use </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__p_d91424e1_d91425e1_d91426e1\">Allowed in dynamic server pages, forms and reports, and in service components that are not self-contained.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__p_d91427e1_d91428e1_d91429e1\">In dynamic server pages, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$valrep</span> can only be used once (before <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$webdefinitions</span>, when the page is initially loaded) to override the declarative ValRep. It cannot be used to dynamically change the ValRep.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"akv1665702559054__topic_d60857e1_d60858e1_d60859e1_d60860e1_d60861e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d932805e227\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"akv1665702559054__p_d91433e1_d91434e1_d91435e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$valrep</span> returns or sets the ValRep list for the specified field in all occurrences in the component. The ValRep list set with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$valrep</span>:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"akv1665702559054__li_d36122e1_d36123e1_d36124e1\">Overrides the ValRep list defined for the widget properties dialog box.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"akv1665702559054__li_d36125e1_d36126e1_d36127e1\">Is reset to the compiled list each time that a component is restarted.(with <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Keep Data in Memory</span> set off )\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"akv1665702559054__li_d36128e1_d36129e1_d36130e1\">Can be overridden for the field in a single occurrence by using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalrep</span>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"akv1665702559054__section_cwy_1jj_zcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d932805e260\">Example: Setting the ValRep for a Radio Group</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example sets the ValRep for the radio group for field\n               GENDER. The underlined semicolon (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>\n</code>) represents the Uniface subfield separator (by default, GOLD ;).</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"akv1665702559054__pre_vwk_bjj_zcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$valrep(GENDER.PERSON) = \"F=Female<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>M=Male<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>N=Not specified\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hxn1665702558407.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvalrep</a><p>Return or set the associative (ValRep) list for an instance of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$valrep Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return or set the ValRep used by a widget for a field. $valrep { ( Field { , List } ) } $valrep { ( Field ) } = List Example: $valrep(COLORS.THEME) = \"R=Red ; G=Green ; B=Blue\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Field name; optional; can be a literal name, a string, or a variable, function, parameter or indirect reference to a field. Field can optionally contain a qualified field name, for example, MYFLD.MYENT . If omitted, the current field is used. List String Associative list that contains the desired ValRep items for the specified field Return Values ValRep list used by a widget for the specified field. Empty string (\"\"), if no ValRep list has been declared or if the field cannot be found. Use Allowed in dynamic server pages, forms and reports, and in service components that are not self-contained. In dynamic server pages, $valrep can only be used once (before $webdefinitions , when the page is initially loaded) to override the declarative ValRep. It cannot be used to dynamically change the ValRep. Description $valrep returns or sets the ValRep list for the specified field in all occurrences in the component. The ValRep list set with $valrep : Overrides the ValRep list defined for the widget properties dialog box. Is reset to the compiled list each time that a component is restarted.(with Keep Data in Memory set off ) Can be overridden for the field in a single occurrence by using $fieldvalrep . Example: Setting the ValRep for a Radio Group The following example sets the ValRep for the radio group for field GENDER. The underlined semicolon ( ; ) represents the Uniface subfield separator (by default, GOLD ;). $valrep(GENDER.PERSON) = \"F=Female ; M=Male ; N=Not specified\" Copy Related Links $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. $fieldvalrep Return or set the associative (ValRep) list for an instance of a field. $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}